data.description: Don't mind the days on market. Buyer couldn't perform. Their loss your gain! Check out this lovely home in Homestead! This adorable 3 bed, 2 bath property offers a 2-car garage, low-care landscape and energy efficiency with solar. Perfectly flowing open layout features neutral tile floor, calming paint, and recessed lighting. Cooking is a delight in this impeccable kitchen boasting neutral tone cabinets, tile backsplash, SS appliances and an island w/a breakfast bar. Have a good night's sleep in this carpeted owner's suite showcasing an ensuite w/dual sinks & a walk-in closet. This serene backyard provides a cozy covered patio and beautiful artificial turf. Take a tour before it's gone!
